Introduction

Newkidd (also stylized as NewKidd) is an eight-member boy group under J-FLO Entertainment. They officially debuted on April 25, 2019, with their self-titled single album "NEWKIDD."

Their name stands for "Newgeneration key of the Dream."

On July 28, 2022, the news of Minwook's addition was announced via Newkidd's official Twitter.
